Business Brief -- Sunrise Technologies Inc.:
   Firm Sees Quarterly Loss;
   Its Stock Price Plummets
The news battered Sunrise stock yesterday in national
over-the-counter trading, where it closed at $13, down $4.50.
   Sunrise declined to estimate the size of the loss. In the
year-earlier first quarter, it earned $700,000, or nine cents
a share, on revenue of $4.1 million.